 Welcome to the DEMO version of AMY'S FUN-2-3 ADVENTURE!

 Amy's Fun-2-3 Adventure is a new commercial educational software package
 from Devasoft for children ages 2 to 6.  Learning number recognition
 and counting skills have never been so much fun before!

 Read the "ReadMe.2" file for a detailed description of the program, and
 the "ReadMe.3" file for a special offer on this program that you can
 get direct from Devasoft for a limited time!

 We hope you enjoy the demo.


 *** MEMORY NOTE:
 ----------------
 AMY'S FUN-2-3 ADVENTURE requires 1 MEG of ram to run.

 TO RUN THE DEMO:

 1) From the CLI:
   a) Put all the files in the same directory (or on the same disk).
   b) CD (change directory) to the directory or disk where the files are.
   c) Type "FUN23DEMO".

 2) From the WorkBench:
   a) Load the WorkBench.
   b) Open the Directory (or disk) where all the Fun23 files are kept.
   c) Double-click on the FUN23DEMO ICON.

 To EXIT the program, press the <ESC> key at any time.





